{
  "message": "perf: remove unused highlight.js and rehype-highlight dependencies\n\nThese dependencies were never imported anywhere in the codebase:\n- highlight.js: The markdown renderer uses react-syntax-highlighter\n  with prism-light, not highlight.js\n- rehype-highlight: Not used - syntax highlighting is done client-side\n  via react-syntax-highlighter, not via rehype plugins\n\nRemoves ~2MB from node_modules and eliminates dead code from\npotential bundle inclusion.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
